  intros A Hcase1 k pre suf red_pre red_suf b
    pre2 child suf2 tail
    outer_pre outer_suf outer_pre' pre' suf' outer_suf'
    pre_out pre2' suf2' suf_out
    Hpre Hsuf Hred_pre Hred_suf Hempty Hpkt Hred_pkt Hb Hred
