Proof.
  unfold recursive_repair_tail_parent_context_ready_hole_case3_output_weak_context.
  intros A k pre1 pre2 child2 suf2 suf1 tail
    pre1' pre2' suf2' suf1' Hctx Hpre_concat Hsuf_concat.
