      A (S k) suf2 suf1 suf2' suf1'
      Hsuf2 Hsuf1 Hsuf2_shape Hsuf_concat)
    as [_ [Hsuf1'_shape Hsuf1']].
  unfold green_of_red_k_context_ready_at. cbn.
  repeat split; try assumption.
  constructor; [exact Hpre1'|constructor|exact Hsuf1'].
Qed.

